      "summary": "Docker daemon 配置片段，仅禁用 ICC（容器间通信），供 Packer 镜像构建阶段注入到集群节点。",
      "tags": ["configuration", "containerization", "infrastructure", "docker", "packer"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:iac/nomad-cluster-disk-image/setup/install-clickhouse-client.sh",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "install-clickhouse-client.sh",
      "filePath": "iac/nomad-cluster-disk-image/setup/install-clickhouse-client.sh",
      "summary": "在 Nomad 集群基础镜像中预装指定版本的 clickhouse-client：从官方 tarball 下载、校验 SHA-512、解压并安装到 /usr/local/bin，同时配置 profile.d 以确保登录 shell 可用。",
      "tags": ["shell", "clickhouse", "installation", "packer", "infrastructure"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 mktemp + trap 模式安全清理临时目录；避免覆盖 POSIX TMPDIR；通过 sha512sum -c 校验标准 checksum 文件。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:iac/nomad-cluster-disk-image/setup/install-cni-plugins.sh",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "install-cni-plugins.sh",
      "filePath": "iac/nomad-cluster-disk-image/setup/install-cni-plugins.sh",
      "summary": "将 containernetworking/plugins 的 CNI 二进制预装到 /opt/cni/bin，使 Nomad 可在 bridge 网络模式下工作；自动识别 amd64/arm64 架构并校验 SHA-256。",
      "tags": ["shell", "cni", "networking", "nomad", "packer", "infrastructure"],
      "complexity": "moderate"
    },
    {
