      "tags": ["shell", "consul", "installation", "tls", "packer", "infrastructure"],
      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "依赖 /opt/gruntwork/bash-commons 中的 assert.sh/log.sh/os.sh 工具库；retry 函数封装最多 5 次重试并保留退出状态。"
